Patch Set 7: Code-Review-2

(4 comments)

I got some problems:
- If I empty the list of constraints, the Save button is not available anymore;
- If I leave a valid_values or range constraint empty, it allows me to save and does not persist any constraint that follows them. It should not allow empty constraints and the backend should also return an error;
- The property type is not being considered when adding a constraint. I believe that only string accepts all the types, the rest has limitations, so the type should be a precondition to add a constraint. Also, when changing the type, the constraints should be cleared.
